{"tid":2166732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司人員 無一個係無辜 以後同黑警同一待遇","createTime":"2020-08-20T14:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T01:21:00.000Z","uid":101392,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"307b2f4735b86a27adb406695dcb41428016ccf2","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人，唔告<br />\n藍絲撞人，唔告<br />\n辛辛苦苦眾籌私人檢控兩條仆街、法庭都批埋<br />\n一個唔該話介入接手 撤控<br />\n以後藍絲、黑警殺人，全部可以肯定無任何後果<br />\n以後見親律政狗，全部杯葛<br />\n律政狗仔女 ， 全部杯葛"},{"pid":"32673763f7c8a3656e1a250d4bf994070af658e4","tid":2166732,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"fcff0ce6efa58cbf73f5add526f55d7e18cc5829","tid":2166732,"uid":123774,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdLP11t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdLP11t.jpg&h=f9393dff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb2f854f4b2e51cdabff5f72b12c190e20960c95","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d79b5a91c893e62a24ece879ac43771dce038b5","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fcff0ce6efa58cbf73f5add526f55d7e18cc5829","tid":2166732,"uid":123774,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdLP11t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdLP11t.jpg&h=f9393dff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改得好好"},{"pid":"e7d1ee8914cc3ad3ca05f38e336db63886508d91","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"黑警係最打人殺人嗰班<br />\n律政狗係包庇佢地犯罪、等佢地無後顧之憂為所欲為嘅人<br />\n等同鼓勵、煽動黑警、藍絲殺人<br />\n一樣咁大罪<br />\n甚至罪責更大"},{"pid":"e40d8b5abbec3ebb03fce4d0c5314bfd017935df","tid":2166732,"uid":305358,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔好話律政司，大律師公會呢？D律師死曬？OMDB呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea6d53bcf133a52b6f59ca659beca3989e3d4c7","tid":2166732,"uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"梁卓然想走扮無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49e85221614f4878f1cc19b6f95b0f25b3960a6","tid":2166732,"uid":288489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"Well said<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e99bb51ec0190aee86be131180245cd0c425f4","tid":2166732,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0dbce89d2dcbea9012fddcfeb7c0e9e4327871","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"律政司人員五大罪狀：<br />\n<br />\n罪狀一：政治逼害義士<br />\n魚蛋革命、反送中運動，數百手足被告暴動<br />\n揀條極重嘅暴動最嚟告義士 令佢地要受牢獄之苦<br />\n失去人生最黃金嘅6、7年<br />\n而家更加用終身監禁嘅國安法<br />\n剝奪義士一生自由<br />\n<br />\n罪狀二：放生藍絲、黑警<br />\n黑警殺人完全一個都唔告<br />\n辛辛苦苦籌錢私人檢控 法庭都批埋<br />\n一個唔該撤控 <br />\n明目張膽鼓勵黑警藍絲繼續殺人<br />\n<br />\n罪狀三：DQ立法會議員：<br />\n等同推翻民主選舉結果，侮辱幾十萬選票嘅民意，剝奪民選議員嘅參政權利<br />\n選舉主任嘅所謂「法律意見」都係律政司俾<br />\nDQ梁游、羅冠聰佢地，就直情係律政司入稟法庭<br />\n<br />\n罪狀四：放生高官<br />\n放生梁振英貪污五千萬：完全無徵詢獨立法律意見，違反程序公義<br />\n<br />\n罪狀五：草擬惡法<br />\n草擬送中法案：律政司法律草擬科負責草擬法案，而「送中法案」就係導致咁多義士頭破血流，甚至義士犧牲以死控訴嘅始作俑者<br />\n草擬蒙面法、動用緊急法取消選舉<br />\n律政司全部有份"},{"pid":"db4d9f3f107dbdb8f0f8d0d0619035c9180638cd","tid":2166732,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"407d3d1df2ce66270723050f939ba37640a4c2c6","tid":2166732,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966092b62d7a0f7458bb0a67b9a4bf73c303c367","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e40d8b5abbec3ebb03fce4d0c5314bfd017935df","tid":2166732,"uid":305358,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔好話律政司，大律師公會呢？D律師死曬？OMDB呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"沒有一個係無辜<br />\n<br />\n但律政司人員肯定最重罪"},{"pid":"2684fca0b58279af438c2024a8acd4d4f3338ff5","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dea6d53bcf133a52b6f59ca659beca3989e3d4c7","tid":2166732,"uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"梁卓然想走扮無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢條友極度仆街 唔可以俾佢走甩"},{"pid":"f70562247043b88df779d88615974d1fc51ef4b6","tid":2166732,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966092b62d7a0f7458bb0a67b9a4bf73c303c367","tid":2166732,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e40d8b5abbec3ebb03fce4d0c5314bfd017935df","tid":2166732,"uid":305358,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔好話律政司，大律師公會呢？D律師死曬？OMDB呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\